<section class="section s3-formula">
  <div class="container--narrow">

    <p class="eyebrow s3-formula__eyebrow">Myers' Cocktail</p>
    <h2 class="s3-formula__heading">The Myers' Cocktail: The Gold Standard Formula</h2>

    <p class="s3-formula__intro">
      Developed by Dr. John Myers in the 1960s, the Myers' Cocktail is the original IV vitamin therapy.
    </p>
    <p class="s3-formula__intro">
      Its time-tested formula provides a powerful, comprehensive blend of essential vitamins and minerals that work synergistically to support your body's foundational health and address a wide range of common health concerns.
    </p>

    <p class="eyebrow s3-formula__ingredients-label">Key Ingredients &amp; Their Benefits:</p>

    <div class="s3-formula__list">

      <div class="s3-formula__item">
        <h3 class="s3-formula__item-title">Vitamin C</h3>
        <p class="s3-formula__item-body">A powerful antioxidant that is crucial for a healthy immune system, protecting cells from damage, and promoting vibrant skin.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-formula__item">
        <h3 class="s3-formula__item-title">B-Complex Vitamins</h3>
        <p class="s3-formula__item-body">The full suite of B vitamins that act as the building blocks of a healthy body, playing a vital role in energy production, brain function, and stress management.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-formula__item">
        <h3 class="s3-formula__item-title">Vitamin B12</h3>
        <p class="s3-formula__item-body">A powerhouse for creating red blood cells and nerve cells, essential for fighting fatigue, sharpening focus, and enhancing mood.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-formula__item">
        <h3 class="s3-formula__item-title">Magnesium</h3>
        <p class="s3-formula__item-body">A vital mineral involved in over 300 bodily processes. It is known to help relax muscles, calm anxiety, and reduce the frequency of migraines.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s3-formula__cta">
      <a href="/myers-cocktail-iv-therapy" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">
        Schedule Now
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

